          "value": "<div xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\">2019 is definitely the year of Linux on√¢‚Ç¨¬¶ the dashboard. This Jaguar is the first car I√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢ve owned with a serious infotainment system, and it√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s opened my eyes to a few things, one of which might be a real Google vulnerability:  serious competition in the map space.</div>",
        },
