          "uri": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<div xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\">I work in AWS√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s Serverless group, and in the process of pulling together my<a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IPOvrK3S3gQ\\">presentation at re:Invent</a>, discovered that I have a lot of opinions on the subject and, while they may well be wrong, are at least well-informed.  You can watch that YouTube, but who√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s got an hour to spare? And anyhow, blogging√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s really my favorite medium, so here we go.  If I tried to glom them all together into one mega-essay it√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢d be brutally long, so let√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s go short-form.</div>",
