          "uri": "http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom",
          "value": "<div xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\">I√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢m in<a href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regina,_Saskatchewan\\">Regina, Saskatchewan</a>with family for the holidays. Someone said √¢‚Ç¨≈ìLet√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s go to a Christmas Eve carol service√¢‚Ç¨¬ù and five of us did that. We went to<a href=\\"http://www.lakeviewchurch.ca/\\">Lakeview United</a>, where √¢‚Ç¨≈ìUnited√¢‚Ç¨¬ù signifies the<a href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Church_of_Canada\\">United Church of Canada</a>, the biggest Protestant denomination up here. It was uplifting and pleasant and sort of sad.  Disclosure: I√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢m not Christian at all; but still.</div>",
